  "body": "Hi, \r\n\r\nI run chain_indexer_test after I update my geth to 1.9.9 \r\n\r\n#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth version: 1.9.9\r\nOS & Version: MacOSX\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\nIt should be PASS.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\n=== RUN   TestChainIndexerSingle\r\n--- FAIL: TestChainIndexerSingle (5.79s)\r\n    chain_indexer_test.go:155: Canonical section count mismatch: have 79, want 78\r\n\r\n#### Try\r\n````\r\nfunc (b *testChainIndexBackend) reorg(headNum uint64) uint64 {\r\n\tfirstChanged := (headNum + 1) / b.indexer.sectionSize\r\n\tif firstChanged < b.stored {\r\n\t\tb.stored = firstChanged\r\n\t}\r\n\treturn b.stored * b.indexer.sectionSize\r\n}\r\n````\r\nI found it can be PASS after I modified\r\n```\r\n firstChanged := headNum / b.indexer.sectionSize to headNum + 1\r\n```\r\nto \r\n```\r\n firstChanged := (headNum + 1) / b.indexer.sectionSize to headNum + 1\r\n```\r\nin chain_indexer_test.go len 206.\r\n\r\nPlease suggest. Thank you.\r\n@zsfelfoldi ",
